Project Description

OpenStreetMap2Oracle is a windows application, which exports OpenStreetMap Data (*.osm - files) to an oracle database. The geometries will be stored in oracle's SDO_GEOMETRY datatype. It is developed in C Sharp with modern WPF - UI.
The application runs with Windows XP, Windows Vista and Windows 7 both in 32Bit and 64Bit. Supported oracle versions are 10gR2 and 11gR2.

How to use this software see Documentation.

You want to get involved in developing this software? See Source Code section.
